thread.title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Kingdom Sci-Tech sees FY 2017 net profit down 71.5 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Kingdom Sci-Tech sees FY 2017 net profit down 71.5 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - shenzhen kingdom sci-tech co ltd

text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - Shenzhen Kingdom Sci-Tech Co Ltd
* Says it sees net profit for FY 2017 to decrease by 71.5 percent
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 235.1 million yuan
* Comments that increased administration expense and financial expense as main reasons for the forecast
